# Keep the Docker build context small + reproducible (the Dockerfile does
# `COPY . .` then builds `rust/Cargo.toml --locked`). Exclude build output, VCS,
# and dev/plan artifacts that don't affect the build.
rust/target/
**/target/
.git/
.github/
plans/
Docs/
docs/
*.bam
*.fq.gz
*.fastq.gz
**/*.md
!rust/README.md
!rust/THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.md
